snippet.textDisplay: How Terry is not included is beyond me... Terry was still playing untill 2017 both Rio and Vidic were finished by 2014. Van dijk will go down as one of the best premier league centre backs no question but the decade ahead will be his decade not the last one. Not to mention Terry is still the highest goal scoring defender in premier league history. Chelsea were also the most successful club in terms of the number of trophies won from 2010-2019 which he would have been captain for most of.
